
These are sketches for a collaborative editor closely following
suggestions taken from the paper "Real time group editors without
Operational transformation" by Oster, Urso, Molli and Imine.

On the base of hastec I established native functions for handling
hashtables. These are a little involved, I think I will use
conditional compilation to avoid using Ptr everywhere.

The server does not actually do anything yet and the client is minimal
at best, but core functions are implemented in Haskell and appear to
work correctly.